### **Automation & Enforcement**

**Recommended Tools:**

1. [**Husky**](https://typicode.github.io/husky) ‚Äì Git hooks management
2. [**commitlint**](https://commitlint.js.org/) ‚Äì Commit message linting
3. [**Commitizen**](https://commitizen-tools.github.io/commitizen/) ‚Äì Interactive commit CLI
4. [**conventional-changelog**](https://github.com/conventional-changelog/conventional-changelog) ‚Äì Automated changelog generation
5. [**semantic-release**](https://semantic-release.gitbook.io/) ‚Äì Automated versioning and releases
6. [**gitmoji-cli**](https://gitmoji.dev/) ‚Äì Emoji commit helper

**Basic Setup Example:**

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install --save-dev @commitlint/cli @commitlint/config-conventional husky

# Configure commitlint
echo "module.exports = {extends: ['@commitlint/config-conventional']}" > commitlint.config.js

# Setup Husky
npx husky install
npx husky add .husky/commit-msg 'npx --no -- commitlint --edit "$1"'
```

